  <p><strong>Farnsworth A:</strong> You people and your slight differences disgust me. I'm going home. Where's that blue box with our universe in it?</p>
  
  <p><strong>Farnsworth 1:</strong>  Oh, you'd like to get back to your evil universe, wouldn't you? And destroy <em>your</em> box with <em>our</em> universe inside it.</p>
  
