  <p>The important thing is not to shout at this point, Vimes told himself. Do not ... what do
  they call it ... go spare? Treat this as a learning exercise. Find out why the world is not
  as you thought it was. Assemble the facts, digest the information, consider the
  implications. <em>Then</em> go spare. But with precision.</p>
