f="http://lesswrong.com/user/MichaelGR/">MichaelGR</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 November 2010 09:09:50PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2wih'>6 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2wih'] = ['5 points', '6 points', '7 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2wih')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2wih" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>It is still an unending source of surprise for me how a few scribbles on a blackboard or on a piece of paper can change the course of human affairs. -Stanislaw Ulam</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2wih"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2wih" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2wih')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2wih" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2wih')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2wih" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/30k/rationality_quotes_november_2010/2wih?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2wih" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2wih')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2wih class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2wih" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_2wih" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_2wih" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2wj6" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2wj6" class="parent"><a name="2wj6" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2wj6" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2wj6" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2wj6" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 November 2010 09:55:52PM</span><span class="votes " >1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2wj6'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_2wj6')">[+] (8 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2wj6" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2wj6" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 November 2010 09:55:52PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2wj6'>1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2wj6'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2wj6')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2wj6" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Can they really? I have my doubts. Most of those scribbles on a blackboard were either an inevitable result of outside forces or would have been made on a different blackboard had they they not been made there. (Although to be fair the butterfly and mere chance will play their part at least some of the time.)</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2wj6"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2wj6" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2wj6')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2wj6" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2wj6')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2wj6" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/30k/rationality_quotes_november_2010/2wj6?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_2wj6" href="#2wih" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2wj6" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2wj6')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2wj6 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2wj6" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_2wj6" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_2wj6" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2wjh" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2wjh" class="parent"><a name="2wjh" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2wjh" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2wjh" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2wjh" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Perplexed/">Perplexed</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 November 2010 10:23:06PM</span><span class="votes " >4 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2wjh'] = ['3 points', '4 points', '5 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_2wjh')">[+] (5 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2wjh" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2wjh" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Perplexed/">Perplexed</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 November 2010 10:23:06PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2wjh'>4 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2wjh'] = ['3 points', '4 points', '5 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2wjh')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2wjh" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Scribbles on maps, particularly in 1815 and 1919, had some largish effects.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2wjh"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2wjh" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2wjh')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2wjh" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2wjh')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2wjh" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/30k/rationality_quotes_november_2010/2wjh?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_2wjh" href="#2wj6" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2wjh" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2wjh')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2wjh class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2wjh" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_2wjh" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_2wjh" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2x4a" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2x4a" class="parent"><a name="2x4a" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2x4a" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2x4a" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2x4a" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/gwern/">gwern</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 November 2010 09:00:55PM</span><span class="votes " >1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2x4a'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_2x4a')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2x4a" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2x4a" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/gwern/">gwern</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 November 2010 09:00:55PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2x4a'>1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2x4a'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2x4a')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2x4a" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>The partitions of Korea and Vietnam are some more recent examples; nor have we seen the last of the largish effects of the former.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2x4a"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2x4a" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2x4a')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2x4a" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2x4a')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2x4a" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/30k/rationality_quotes_november_2010/2x4a?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_2x4a" href="#2wjh" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2x4a" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2x4a')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2x4a class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2x4a" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2wk8" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2wk8" class="parent"><a name="2wk8" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2wk8" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2wk8" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2wk8" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/DanArmak/">DanArmak</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 November 2010 10:53:54PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " >22 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2wk8'] = ['21 points', '22 points', '23 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_2wk8')">[+] (3 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2wk8" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2wk8" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/DanArmak/">DanArmak</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 November 2010 10:53:54PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2wk8'>22 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2wk8'] = ['21 points', '22 points', '23 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2wk8')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2wk8" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>In 1923, England and France divided between them the previously Turkish territories of what are modern Syria, Lebanon and Israel/Palestine. They drew a pencil line on a map to mark the treaty border.</p>

<p>It turned out that the thickness of the pencil line itself was several hundred meters on the ground. In 1964, Israel fought a battle with Syria over that land.</p>

<p>People were killed because someone neglected to sharpen their pencil. That's "scribbles on a piece of paper" for you.</p>

<p>Ref: <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=Q0suiJ7Gj1QC&amp;pg=PA741&amp;lpg=PA741&amp;dq=thickness+of+pencil+line+on+map+israel+syria&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=82vMMd2j-S&amp;sig=a5SLDXgtFPzouqlZXnMefH4GKxQ&amp;hl=en&amp;ei=jDfTTMvYCpe8jAeepP2QDg&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=book_result&amp;ct=result&amp;resnum=1&amp;ved=0CBIQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&amp;q=thickness%20of%20pencil%20line%20on%20map%20israel%20syria&amp;f=false" rel="nofollow">a book found by Google</a>. I originally learned about this from an Israeli plaque at the Dan River preserve near the border.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2wk8"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2wk8" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2wk8')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2wk8" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2wk8')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2wk8" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/30k/rationality_quotes_november_2010/2wk8?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_2wk8" href="#2wjh" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2wk8" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2wk8')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2wk8 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2wk8" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_2wk8" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_2wk8" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2wke" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2wke" class="parent"><a name="2wke" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2wke" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2wke" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2wke" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 November 2010 11:02:26PM</span><span class="votes " >4 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2wke'] = ['3 points', '4 points', '5 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_2wke')">[+] (2 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2wke" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2wke" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 November 2010 11:02:26PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2wke'>4 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2wke'] = ['3 points', '4 points', '5 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2wke')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2wke" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
  <p>People were killed because someone neglected to sharpen their pencil. That's "scribbles on a piece of paper" for you.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>I suppose it would be in bad taste to find that rather amusing. Or at least to admit it.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2wke"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2wke" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2wke')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2wke" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2wke')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2wke" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/30k/rationality_quotes_november_2010/2wke?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_2wke" href="#2wk8" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2wke" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2wke')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2wke class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2wke" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_2wke" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_2wke" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2ztl" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2ztl" class="parent"><a name="2ztl" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2ztl" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2ztl" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2ztl" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Drawbacks/">Drawbacks</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">23 November 2010 10:23:09PM</span><span class="votes " >1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2ztl'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_2ztl')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2ztl" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2ztl" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Drawbacks/">Drawbacks</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">23 November 2010 10:23:09PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2ztl'>1 point</span><script type="text/j