ar"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2web" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/XiXiDu/">XiXiDu</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 November 2010 12:37:19PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2web'>14 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2web'] = ['13 points', '14 points', '15 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2web')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2web" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>This is a bit long for a rationality quote and isn't really a quote but short enough and worth the read: <a href="http://www.davideagleman.com/descent.html" rel="nofollow">The most poetic and convincing argument for striving for posthumanity</a> (via aleph.se).</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_2web"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_2web" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2web')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_2web" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_2web')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_2web" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/30k/rationality_quotes_november_2010/2web?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_2web" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_2web')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_2web class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_2web" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_2web" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_2web" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_2wz9" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_2wz9" class="parent"><a name="2wz9" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_2wz9" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_2wz9" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_2wz9" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Pavitra/">Pavitra</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 No